<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2887] Improvements and refactor for HBaseFsck tool</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2887</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Refactored the way the HBaseFsck tool works &amp;#8211; it now loads all the info it can find into RAM first, and then looks over the in-memory structures for inconsistencies. It&apos;s still a work in progress, but detects more kinds of problems now (eg multiple assignment, etc) and has some very basic functional tests.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
