&lt;p&gt;Bunch of changes to the HBaseFsck tool to detect a wider variety of issues and to make it easier to add &quot;fix&quot; support for these problems in the future.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2887&quot; title=&quot;Improvements and refactor for HBaseFsck tool&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-2887&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-2887&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
