&lt;p&gt;Diff: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.cloudera.org/r/418/diff&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://review.cloudera.org/r/418/diff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


